Sentencas: Materials of the K2NiF4 structure type, and in particular those with a stoichiometry of LaxSr2-xFeO4-delta, have been investigated as possible cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Thermal stability and conduction properties of the LaxSr2-xFeO4+δ system

Sentencas: A range of compositions was studied and careful attention was paid to the oxygen stoichiometry.
Titulo: Thermal stability and conduction properties of the LaxSr2-xFeO4+δ system

Sentencas: It was evident from the results that oxygen excess was incorporated into the lattice and that the DC conductivity was significantly influenced by oxygen content.
Titulo: Thermal stability and conduction properties of the LaxSr2-xFeO4+δ system

Sentencas: Investigation of the materials at elevated temperature, indicated that at the operating temperatures of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFCs), these materials would remain stable with respect to temperature.
Titulo: Thermal stability and conduction properties of the LaxSr2-xFeO4+δ system
